OL,3,CChanging time of day for asthma
OL,4,Cmedication 'could help symptoms'
OL,6,FExperts said their study, published in
OL,7,Fthe journal Thorax, is the first to
OL,8,Fshow the importance of co-ordinating
OL,9,Fasthma treatment with a person's body
OL,10,Fclock ` also known as circadian
OL,11,Frhythms.
OL,13,FResearchers examined 21 patients with
OL,14,Fasthma who were asked to take their
OL,15,Fmedication in a different way.
OL,17,FOnce they had completed a week of one
OL,18,Ftreatment pattern they then switched
OL,19,Fto another until they had all
OL,20,Fcompleted each of the three treatment
OL,21,Fpatterns.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
