OL,3,CChanging time of day for asthma
OL,4,Cmedication 'could help symptoms'
OL,6,FThese treatment patterns included a
OL,7,Fonce-daily dose of 400mg between 8am
OL,8,Fand 9am, a once-daily dose between 3pm
OL,9,Fand 4pm, with the final group taking
OL,10,Fhalf the dose between 8am and 9am and
OL,11,Fa second half dose between 8pm and 9pm
OL,12,F` the "usual" pattern of dosing in the
OL,13,FUK.
OL,15,FThey each had a two-week "washout"
OL,16,Fperiod between each dosing regime.
OL,26,@tD@GOUtD@MO]wD@ZOUwD@bO]
