OL,3,CChanging time of day for asthma
OL,4,Cmedication 'could help symptoms'
OL,6,FWhile the research team found all
OL,7,Fregimes appeared to improve asthma
OL,8,Fcontrol, the once-daily afternoon dose
OL,9,Fappeared to improve night-time lung
OL,10,Ffunction and those on this regime
OL,11,Fappeared to have better blood
OL,12,Feosinophil counts ` a key biomarker
OL,13,Ffor airway inflammation.
OL,15,F"Mid-afternoon dosing of inhaled
OL,16,Fbeclomethasone may lead to better
OL,17,Fclinical outcomes without increasing
OL,18,Fsteroid-related morbidity or costs,"
OL,19,Fthey said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@dO]
