OL,4,Cmedication 'could help symptoms'
OL,6,FExperts called for further larger
OL,7,Ftrials to confirm the findings.
OL,9,FStudy lead Dr Hannah Durrington, from
OL,10,Fthe University of Manchester and
OL,11,FManchester University NHS Foundation
OL,12,FTrust, said: "Up to three-quarters of
OL,13,Fpatients experience worsening symptoms
OL,14,Fovernight and up to 80% of fatal
OL,15,Fasthma attacks occur at night.
OL,26,@tD@NOU
