OL,6,F"Inhaler medication is vital to keep
OL,7,Fyour asthma under control. It's easy
OL,8,Fto forget that asthma attacks can be
OL,9,Ffatal and require daily management in
OL,10,Fthe form of inhalers to stay healthy."
